This repository contains sample projects illustrating usage of the Spring Mobile project.

Samples include:
- lite-showcase, demonstrating the capabilities of the Spring Mobile "Lite" DeviceResolver for server-side device detection.
- wurfl-showcase, demonstrating the capabilities of the Spring Mobile WURFL DeviceResolver for expanded server-side device detection.
 
See the README in each sub directory for information on the sample and instructions on how to run it.